name: SYNTHCITY - CONSPIRAMID
description:
LOCATION: CONSPIRAMID

“The CONSPIRAMID is a mysterious relic spawned and created by numerous conspiracy theories.
All of these theories, confirmed or deemed fake, are materialised and realised in this building.
The building is shaped like a pyramid, has fantastic internet, is run by lizard-people, offers pizza, has a film studio and is located on a floating flat rock."

By Die-Jay-Cee
